  "body": "\n\n<div class=\"oahs-outer\">\n<div class=\"oahs-inner\">\n LEFT: Text \n<div class=\"oahs-text\">\n H1 — italic accent, left-aligned, RDash signature \n<h1 class=\"oahs-h1\">\n<em class=\"oahs-h1-em\">One platform,</em><br/>\n        every Australian site.\n      </h1>\n Subline \n<p class=\"oahs-sub\">\n        Manage projects, procurement, labour, and finance across every site — without stitching multiple tools together.\n      </p>\n Single CTA \n<a class=\"oahs-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">\n        Book a Free Demo\n        <svg fill=\"none\" height=\"14\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" viewbox=\"0 0 14 14\" width=\"14\"><path d=\"M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n Social proof \n<div class=\"oahs-proof\">\n<div class=\"oahs-avatars\">\n<div class=\"oahs-av oahs-av1\">SP</div>\n<div class=\"oahs-av oahs-av2\">JS</div>\n<div class=\"oahs-av oahs-av3\">MD</div>\n<div class=\"oahs-av oahs-av4\">RC</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"oahs-proof-txt\"><strong>500+ construction teams</strong> already run their sites on SiteFlow</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n RIGHT: Provided image (same src as original hero) \n<div class=\"oahs-imgcol\">\n<img alt=\"SiteFlow construction management software dashboard for Australian builders\" class=\"oahs-img\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"900\" src=\"/images/recon/Adobe-Express-file.webp\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"oaud-outer\">\n<div class=\"oaud-inner\">\n HEADER \n<div class=\"oaud-hdr\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"oaud-eyebrow\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"oaud-eyebrow-dot\"></span>\n        Who SiteFlow is built for\n      </div>\n<h2 class=\"oaud-h2\">\n        Integrated Construction Software Platform for<br/>\n<span class=\"oaud-h2-em\">every Australian builder.</span>\n</h2>\n</div>\n<p class=\"oaud-sub\">\n      Whether you run five house builds, manage subcontractors across multiple sites, or track labour on civil projects — SiteFlow handles every workflow from one place.\n    </p>\n</div>\n TILES \n<div class=\"oaud-grid\">\n Tile 1: Interior Designers → Interior Companies page \n<a class=\"oaud-tile\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/app-for-interior-designing/\">\n<img alt=\"Interior designer reviewing project plans on site\" class=\"oaud-tile-img\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Your-paragraph-text.webp\" width=\"600\"/>\n<div class=\"oaud-tile-panel\">\n<h3 class=\"oaud-tile-h3\">Interior Designers</h3>\n<p class=\"oaud-tile-desc\">Manage design-to-execution workflows, vendors, and client updates from one place.</p>\n<span class=\"oaud-tile-link\">\n          Learn more\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n</a>\n Tile 2: Builders → Builders &amp; Developers page \n<a class=\"oaud-tile\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/erp-software-for-builders-and-developers/\">\n<img alt=\"Residential builder managing house projects\" class=\"oaud-tile-img\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Your-paragraph-text-3.webp\" width=\"600\"/>\n<div class=\"oaud-tile-panel\">\n<h3 class=\"oaud-tile-h3\">Builders</h3>\n<p class=\"oaud-tile-desc\">Manage multiple builds at once with full cost and schedule visibility.</p>\n<span class=\"oaud-tile-link\">\n          Learn more\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n</a>\n Tile 3: Civil Contractors → Civil Contractors page \n<a class=\"oaud-tile\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/civil-contractors/\">\n<img alt=\"Civil contractor supervising road project\" class=\"oaud-tile-img\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Your-paragraph-text-2.webp\" width=\"600\"/>\n<div class=\"oaud-tile-panel\">\n<h3 class=\"oaud-tile-h3\">Civil Contractors</h3>\n<p class=\"oaud-tile-desc\">Connect site and office teams in real time across multiple projects.</p>\n<span class=\"oaud-tile-link\">\n          Learn more\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"obnt-outer\">\n<div class=\"obnt-inner\">\n HEADER \n<div class=\"obnt-hdr\">\n<div class=\"obnt-eyebrow\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"obnt-eyebrow-dot\"></span>\n      The SiteFlow Platform\n    </div>\n<h2 class=\"obnt-h2\">\n      Your platform for the\n      <span class=\"obnt-h2-em\">future of construction.</span>\n</h2>\n<a class=\"obnt-hdr-link\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/\">\n      Explore all modules\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n</div>\n ROW 1: 2 TALL CARDS \n<div class=\"obnt-row1\">\n Big card 1: AI Features — link unchanged \n<a class=\"obnt-bigcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-bigcard-img-wrap\">\n<img alt=\"SiteFlow AI-powered construction features\" class=\"obnt-bigcard-img\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Untitled-design-1.webp\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obnt-bigcard-body\">\n<span class=\"obnt-bigcard-eyebrow\">AI Features</span>\n<h3 class=\"obnt-bigcard-h3\">Build smarter with AI-powered capabilities</h3>\n<p class=\"obnt-bigcard-desc\">Automate daily reports, get early cost overrun warnings, and let SiteFlow AI handle the routine — so your team stays focused on the work.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-bigcard-link\">\n          Learn more\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n</a>\n Big card 2: Platform → Project Management Software \n<a class=\"obnt-bigcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/construction-project-management-software/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-bigcard-img-wrap\">\n<img alt=\"SiteFlow construction management platform\" class=\"obnt-bigcard-img\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Untitled-design-2.webp\" width=\"1200\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"obnt-bigcard-body\">\n<span class=\"obnt-bigcard-eyebrow\">SiteFlow Platform</span>\n<h3 class=\"obnt-bigcard-h3\">Drive better margins with real-time project data</h3>\n<p class=\"obnt-bigcard-desc\">Connect every team from site to office on one platform. Make data-driven decisions that improve efficiency and reduce financial risk across every project.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-bigcard-link\">\n          Learn more\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div> /row1 \n ROW 2: 4 MODULE CARDS \n<div class=\"obnt-row2\">\n Module 1: Project Execution → Project Planning \n<a class=\"obnt-modcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/construction-project-planning-software/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-mod-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"14\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"14\"></rect>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"obnt-mod-h4\">Project Execution</h4>\n<p class=\"obnt-mod-desc\">Build confidently with progress tracking, quality checks, and daily reporting all connected in one place.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-mod-link\">\n        Learn more\n        <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</a>\n Module 2: Cost Management → Financial Management \n<a class=\"obnt-modcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/construction-financial-management-software/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-mod-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"2\" y2=\"22\"></line>\n<path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"obnt-mod-h4\">Cost Management</h4>\n<p class=\"obnt-mod-desc\">Drive predictable outcomes with real-time visibility into budgets, vendor bills, and live project P&amp;L.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-mod-link\">\n        Learn more\n        <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</a>\n Module 3: Resource Management → Labour Management \n<a class=\"obnt-modcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/construction-labour-management-software/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-mod-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path>\n<circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path>\n<path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"obnt-mod-h4\">Resource Management</h4>\n<p class=\"obnt-mod-desc\">Track labour with GPS attendance, manage subcontractors, and run payroll from verified site data.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-mod-link\">\n        Learn more\n        <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</a>\n Module 4: Procurement → Procurement Management \n<a class=\"obnt-modcard\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/construction-procurement-management-software/\">\n<div class=\"obnt-mod-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z\"></path>\n<line x1=\"3\" x2=\"21\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line>\n<path d=\"M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"obnt-mod-h4\">Procurement</h4>\n<p class=\"obnt-mod-desc\">Raise POs, match vendor bills to deliveries, and keep material costs under control across every project.</p>\n<span class=\"obnt-mod-link\">\n        Learn more\n        <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div> /row2 \n</div> /inner \n</div> /outer \n\n<div class=\"ocls-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocls-card\">\n<div class=\"ocls-inner\">\n LEFT: Stat headline \n<div class=\"ocls-left\">\n<div class=\"ocls-eyebrow\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocls-eyebrow-dot\"></span>\n      Trusted across Australia\n    </div>\n<h2 class=\"ocls-h2\">\n      From Bondi to Perth —\n      <span class=\"ocls-h2-em\">builders run their sites on SiteFlow.</span>\n</h2>\n</div>\n RIGHT: Image strips \n<div class=\"ocls-right\">\n<div class=\"ocls-strip\">\n<img alt=\"Construction companies using SiteFlow\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"120\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Website-icons-banner-2025-1.webp\" width=\"800\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocls-strip\">\n<img alt=\"Construction companies using SiteFlow\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"120\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/images/recon/Website-icons-banner-2025.webp\" width=\"800\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> /inner \n</div> /card \n</div> /outer \n\n<div class=\"oils-outer\">\n<div class=\"oils-inner\">\n LEFT \n<div class=\"oils-left\">\n<div class=\"oils-eyebrow\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"oils-eyebrow-dot\"></span>\n      We’ve got your back\n    </div>\n<h2 class=\"oils-h2\">Get support from construction experts</h2>\n<p class=\"oils-sub\">Our team understands the Australian construction industry — from SOP Act compliance to GPS attendance on civil sites. We are here when you need us.</p>\n<a class=\"oils-btn\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/contact/\">\n      Book a Free Demo\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n</div>\n RIGHT \n<div class=\"oils-right\">\n Row 1: Help Centre \n<a class=\"oils-row\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/help/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"oils-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path>\n<line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12.01\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"17\"></line>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oils-row-text\">\n<h3 class=\"oils-row-h3\">\n          Help Centre\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</h3>\n<p class=\"oils-row-desc\">Step-by-step guides, video walkthroughs, and FAQs covering every SiteFlow module — available any time your team needs them.</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n Row 2: Integrations \n<a class=\"oils-row\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/integrations/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"oils-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"15\" y=\"3\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"2\" y=\"14\"></rect>\n<rect height=\"7\" rx=\"1\" width=\"7\" x=\"15\" y=\"14\"></rect>\n<line x1=\"9\" x2=\"15\" y1=\"6.5\" y2=\"6.5\"></line>\n<line x1=\"9\" x2=\"15\" y1=\"17.5\" y2=\"17.5\"></line>\n<line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oils-row-text\">\n<h3 class=\"oils-row-h3\">\n          Integrations\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</h3>\n<p class=\"oils-row-desc\">Connect SiteFlow to Tally, Zoho Books, and the tools your team already uses. No double entry, no manual exports.</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n Row 3: Contact Us \n<a class=\"oils-row\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/contact/\">\n<div class=\"oils-icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oils-row-text\">\n<h3 class=\"oils-row-h3\">\n          Talk to Our Team\n          <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg>\n</h3>\n<p class=\"oils-row-desc\">Speak with a real SiteFlow expert — not a chatbot. Get a personalised walkthrough built around your project type and team size.</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div> /right \n</div> /inner \n</div> /outer \n\n<div class=\"oaai-outer\">\n<div class=\"oaai-inner\">\n<div class=\"oaai-grid\">\n<div class=\"oaai-left\">\n<div class=\"oaai-badge\">\n<div class=\"oaai-badge-dot-wrap\">\n<div class=\"oaai-badge-ping\"></div>\n<div class=\"oaai-badge-dot\"></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"oaai-badge-txt\">SiteFlow AI — Now Live</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"oaai-h2\">\n          Your Projects,<br/>\n<span class=\"oaai-h2-em\">Managed by AI.</span>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"oaai-sub\">SiteFlow is not just a data entry tool. The AI built into your workflow analyses site activity, writes reports, and recommends actions automatically — before problems reach you.</p>\n<div class=\"oaai-features\">\n<div class=\"oaai-feat\">\n<div class=\"oaai-feat-icon\">🤖</div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-title\">AI-Powered Daily Reports</p>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-desc\">SiteFlow AI compiles your daily progress report with corrective recommendations — no manual typing needed.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-feat\">\n<div class=\"oaai-feat-icon\">💬</div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-title\">WhatsApp Updates, Logged by AI</p>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-desc\">Your team sends a photo or note on WhatsApp. AI processes it and records the data directly into SiteFlow.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-feat\">\n<div class=\"oaai-feat-icon\">📐</div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-title\">AI-Assisted BOQ and Estimation</p>\n<p class=\"oaai-feat-desc\">AI builds your BOQ and variation estimates using past Australian project data and your live rate library — protecting your margin from the first quote.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-db-wrap\">\n<div class=\"oaai-db\">\n<div class=\"oaai-chrome\">\n<div class=\"oaai-chrome-dots\">\n<div class=\"oaai-chrome-dot\" style=\"background:#ff5f57\"></div>\n<div class=\"oaai-chrome-dot\" style=\"background:#febc2e\"></div>\n<div class=\"oaai-chrome-dot\" style=\"background:#28c840\"></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"oaai-chrome-title\">SiteFlow AI Assistant</span>\n<span class=\"oaai-chrome-badge\">● Live</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-body\">\n<div class=\"oaai-msg-user\">\n<div class=\"oaai-msg-user-bubble\">\n                Give me today’s progress report for Riverside Apartments — Sydney and flag anything that needs action.\n              </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-thinking\">\n<div class=\"oaai-thinking-av\">✦</div>\n<span class=\"oaai-thinking-txt\">SiteFlow AI is analysing site data…</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-msg-ai\">\n<div class=\"oaai-msg-ai-av\">✦</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-msg-ai-bubble\">\n<div class=\"oaai-line oaai-line-1\">\n<span class=\"oaai-chip\" style=\"background:#ede9fe;color:#7c3aed\">Report</span>\n<span><strong>Riverside Apartments — Sydney</strong> — today’s progress 2.4% vs 3.8% target. Cumulative 58%.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-line oaai-line-2\">\n<span class=\"oaai-chip\" style=\"background:#fef3c7;color:#b45309\">Risk</span>\n<span>Structural frame is 4 days behind. Practical completion shifts by <strong>9 days</strong>.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-line oaai-line-3\">\n<span class=\"oaai-chip\" style=\"background:#fee2e2;color:#dc2626\">Stock</span>\n<span>Reinforcing steel at 6 tonnes — <strong>insufficient</strong> for next week’s slab pour. Raise PO immediately.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-line oaai-line-4\">\n<span class=\"oaai-chip\" style=\"background:#d1fae5;color:#059669\">Action</span>\n<span>Add 4 carpenters by Wednesday. Issue Progress Claim #5 — <strong>A$318,000 incl. GST</strong> — before Friday cut-off.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-line oaai-line-5\">\n<span class=\"oaai-chip\" style=\"background:#ede9fe;color:#7c3aed\">Margin</span>\n<span>Estimated margin holds at <strong>16.8%</strong> if corrective action is taken this week.<span class=\"oaai-cursor\"></span></span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oaai-input\">\n<span class=\"oaai-input-txt\">Ask SiteFlow AI about your Australian projects…</span>\n<span class=\"oaai-input-btn\">Send →</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"oarv-outer\">\n<div class=\"oarv-inner\">\n HEADER \n<div class=\"oarv-hdr\">\n<div class=\"oarv-eyebrow\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"oarv-ey-dot\"></span>\n<span class=\"oarv-ey-txt\">Verified Australian customers</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"oarv-h2\">Reviews and <span class=\"oarv-h2-em\">ratings.</span></h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oarv-grid\">\n ══ LEFT — RATING PANEL ══ \n<div class=\"oarv-panel\">\n Big score \n<div class=\"oarv-score-row\">\n<span class=\"oarv-score-num\">4.8</span>\n<div class=\"oarv-score-right\">\n<div aria-label=\"4.8 out of 5 stars\" class=\"oarv-score-stars\">\n<svg fill=\"#f59e0b\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polygon points=\"12,2 15.09,8.26 22,9.27 17,14.14 18.18,21.02 12,17.77 5.82,21.02 7,14.14 2,9.27 8.91,8.26\"></polygon></svg>\n<svg fill=\"#f59e0b\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polygon points=\"12,2 15.09,8.26 22,9.27 17,14.14 18.18,21.02 12,17.77 5.82,21.02 7,14.14 2,9.27 8.91,8.26\"></polygon></svg>\n<svg fill=\"#f59e0b\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polygon points=\"12,2 15.09,8.26 22,9.27 17,14.14 18.18,21.02 12,17.77 5.82,21.02 7,14.14 2,9.27 8.91,8.26\"></polygon></svg>\n<svg fill=\"#f59e0b\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polygon points=\"12,2 15.09,8.26 22,9.27 17,14.14 18.18,21.02 12,17.77 5.82,21.02 7,14.14 2,9.27 8.91,8.26\"></polygon></svg>\n<svg fill=\"#f59e0b\" opacity=\"0.75\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polygon points=\"12,2 15.09,8.26 22,9.27 17,14.14 18.18,21.02 12,17.77 5.82,21.02 7,14.14 2,9.27 8.91,8.26\"></polygon></svg>\n</div>\n<span class=\"oarv-score-lbl\">Based on 10,000+ companies</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"oarv-div\"></div>\n Sub-rating bars \n<div class=\"oarv-subrats\">\n<div class=\"oarv-subrat\">\n<div class=\"oarv-subrat-top\">\